snippet.title: 1080HDMovieTrailers
snippet.description: http://QuickMovieInfo.com ... Thanks for checking out the 1080HDMovieTrailers Channel. We love movie trailers and are striving to bring you the latest clips in the best possible HD quality (720 minimum, 1080 when available). We adjust the brightness of every trailer, so that our videos have the most-ideal picture quality. These are all the official movie trailers/clips and we never add those annoying comment overlays to our videos. Our goal is to provide you with the most-recent movie trailers/clips with the best quality. If you have any comments/suggestions, please let us know :) These trailers are never ripped from another site and we have obtained access to these trailers﻿ (i.e. have gotten prior permission) from the respective film/tv studio (who are the copyright owner of the contents within the video!)
